        {
            "title": "〈熱門股〉建準受惠AI伺服器需求旺3月、Q1營收創高 周漲逾1成",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">散熱廠<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"建準\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:建準;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/建準\">建準</a> (2421-TW) 受惠 AI 伺服器需求強勁，出貨動能增溫，帶動 3 月營收 19.18 億、第一季營收 50.19 億元，分別創單月、單季新高紀錄，激勵建準本周大漲逾 1 成。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">建準本周股價上漲 15.1%，周五 (10 日) 以 141 元作收，同步收復 5 日線、月線及年線。至於三大法人籌碼動向，本周合計賣超 457 張。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">建準 3 月營收 19.18 億元，月增 44.92%，年增 22.46%；累計今年第一季營收 50.19 億元，季增 2.06%，年增 20.6%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-7e310c3a-fb05-3e05-a68f-5ec45f8351a1-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">建準積極從傳統散熱風扇供應商，轉型為整合散熱解決方案供應商，並積極跨足液冷散熱領域，液冷散熱也為建準今年重點布局產品。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">為因應液冷散熱需求，建準指出，相關產能已陸續到位，新北研發中心及中國惠州廠均建置完成，水冷板已於第一季量產出貨。此外，CDU 也已排定出貨時程，初期優先鎖定 Tier 2 與非主流 GPU、ASIC 客戶，預計今年上半年導入 In-Rack 產品，下半年則將推出 In-Row 解決方案。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"建準日 K 線圖\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"500\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/FOBfq5oNS702FpnbHArZyA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTgyOA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/cnyes_hk_559/e8a57a7341d988d71e9aaa342482f235\" width=\"580\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:580px\">建準日 K 線圖</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"> </p><p class=\"mb-module-gap read-more-vendor break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span>更多鉅亨報導</span><br/>•<a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"〈熱門股〉建準Q4及明年展望樂觀 周漲逾1成創新天價\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:〈熱門股〉建準Q4及明年展望樂觀 周漲逾1成創新天價;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6226331?utm_source=yahoo&amp;utm_medium=RSS&amp;utm_campaign=relate\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">〈熱門股〉建準Q4及明年展望樂觀 周漲逾1成創新天價</a><br/>•<a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"建準看好各事業群明年成長 水冷板明年Q1量產\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:建準看好各事業群明年成長 水冷板明年Q1量產;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6222965?utm_source=yahoo&amp;utm_medium=RSS&amp;utm_campaign=relate\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">建準看好各事業群明年成長 水冷板明年Q1量產</a></p></div>",
